Accent Red color #eb0028
accent new color yellow #FFC829 or #fdbf04

Shipper old bg: rgba(235, 0, 40, 0.9)

Shipper new bg: rgba(9, 4, 68, 0.9) or  #090444

Masking an image especially png with color

.icon {
  width: 24px;  /* Adjust size as needed */
  height: 24px; /* Adjust size as needed */
  background-color: blue; /* The desired blue color */
  -webkit-mask-image: url("path/to/your/icon.png"); /* Safari */
  mask-image: url("path/to/your/icon.png");
  -webkit-mask-size: contain; /* or cover, auto, etc. - Experiment! */
  mask-size: contain;
  -webkit-mask-repeat: no-repeat; /* Safari */
  mask-repeat: no-repeat;
  -webkit-mask-position: center; /* Safari */
  mask-position: center;
}

.image {
